{"tid":1475774,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【要求增援】獨立調查委員會成立前一定要整理好","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T14:31:49.000Z","uid":36735,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"417bba479b99bbe9d617cca30b37a08632ed238d","tid":1475774,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「黑警濫權實權」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由 69 到而家，黑警一次比一次過份，一次比一次暴力，甚至警黑合作都可以唔當做一回事！我地絕對唔可以容忍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係成立獨立調查委員會之前，我地一定要建立好呢個資料庫，有強而有力既證據去指證同追究所有黑警！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早係 19 日前，我建立左個「黑警濫權資料庫」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372532/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372532/page/1</a><br />\n希望將黑警既罪證全部記低！而家已經有幾位手足<span style=\"color: orange;\">每日馬不停蹄</span>將黑警既事蹟放上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">中文版 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KKLbyI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KKLbyI&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=dcf58738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KKLbyI</a><br />\n英文版 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KQ97kt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KQ97kt&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=c4074647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KQ97kt</a><br />\n資料庫 database <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KNVMsQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KNVMsQ&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=443c3586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KNVMsQ</a></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n過往應該有好多唔同既巴絲打都有做過同類既野，不過好多 upload 左一陣已經無再更新 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我地未必做得最好最易睇，但係<span style=\"color: orange;\">我地勝力夠勤力</span>！各位手足每日收工番到屋企即刻開電腦搵料搵新聞再記錄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地希望集合大家既努力整合呢個資料庫，無論你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">想提供黑警證據<br />\n想一齊編輯呢個「黑警濫權實錄」<br />\n可以幫手翻譯<br />\n提供任何建議</span></strong></span><br />\n都歡迎你地加入一定整合呢個資料庫 ，請你 tg 我 <a href=\"https://t.me/Dllmpopo999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDllmpopo999&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=5bfde8d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dllmpopo999</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWr41Sf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWr41Sf.png&h=59d08e16&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n鄭柏林呢條撚樣記唔記得？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dY9Khrd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdY9Khrd.png&h=076012c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被插眼既手足係咪要幫佢追究？</span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXvEQMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXvEQMe.png&h=ada880dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">手足比人打到咁係咪唔可以原諒？</span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKSjQMf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKSjQMf.png&h=5d0dc8d3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有黑警一定要以眼還眼！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警無一個係無辜，當日既所作所為，你地一定要還</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"a2475a072666964f2657ba886280d7a2db5a1a8d","tid":1475774,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afe9ecea4a18dd3f6452a52c630939c75dc27df4","tid":1475774,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEEY6mV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEEY6mV.jpg&h=128a98eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YXG38B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YXG38B.jpg&h=d14afc11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"466167ea0d7425fd3daf3618ed27abbf9525315e","tid":1475774,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"仲有乜好調查呀<br />\n好明顯全部黑警有罪啦"},{"pid":"9f8c011472e481a9f33c9069619b887039da8b29","tid":1475774,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大審判將會嚟到"},{"pid":"d6234cc95105261f04868f8bd4180c2bd850277c","tid":1475774,"uid":149225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"期待緊黑警被清算嘅畫面！！！"},{"pid":"a022ce7cdf8e4864623192d5214d8b9472cf1936","tid":1475774,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:10:38.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a24bce121186066999ba6ea9ae8355347bce69","tid":1475774,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d1079ec67a2df2de9198be871156382e4c1ad2d5","tid":1475774,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"bookmarked + push"},{"pid":"d06cd4ae8a0039a5edc297cfc778ab299ae13e46","tid":1475774,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"27d4c20f9e626edc15a1caeb6ef0b5ff0e9ac9c2","tid":1475774,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"push 重整歷史時序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a61eaf2775f039896b4f07d9acd2705309cb6f4","tid":1475774,"uid":36761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:22:17.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追究警隊嚴重瀆職"},{"pid":"eabea52e401e8cefc9b59b3364eaf5bde6f92e2a","tid":1475774,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"52ad7a47db7d71f50b6e298a79b38416daeaf308","tid":1475774,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:31:25.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過申請禁制令<br />\n將嗰啲濫權犯法嘅警員停職?<br />\n<br />\n【法律JJ】如何用法律去限制警隊濫權<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380667</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>grounds:</ins></strong><br />\n基本法28條<br />\n香港居民的人身自由不受侵犯。&nbsp;<br />\n香港居民不受任意或非法逮捕、拘留、監禁。禁止任意或非法搜查居民的身體、剝奪或限制居民的人身自由。禁止對居民施行酷刑、任意或非法剝奪居民的生命。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>facts</strong></ins>:<br />\n1. 警察非法拘捕 (例如影相告阻差辦工/襲警)<br />\n2. 警察惡意拘捕 (大部份被捕人士都係被拘捕後無條件釋放)<br />\n3. 警察犯法無監管 (拘捕示威人士後毆打佢地, 示威者已經離開緊繼續攻擊)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Application</ins></strong> (禁制令/ 司法覆核)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 禁止明顯犯刑事, 而警察內部無對佢地作出調查嘅警員繼續職務(停職)。<br />\n2. 在處理公眾集會時，禁止沒有展示能識別身份的警員執行職務。(未必要係委任證或警員編號, 但要有明顯睇到嘅ID no., 事後可以搵返係邊一位警員)<br />\n3. 警隊條例需要加入實質有效監察權力的條文。</span><br />\n<br />\n尤其係禁制令<br />\n1. 暫時將某啲警員停職, 並沒有 irreversible consequency.&nbsp;<br />\n2. 繼續比佢地行駛警權, 好大機會會對市民造成irreversible damage。(好多影片可以做證)<br />\n3. 禁制令可以緊急申請。"},{"pid":"553b96f598efd1b2806197adf1592fd053f35368","tid":1475774,"uid":93124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:38:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0087774588191a9110a102a40b754dc75c53e23d","tid":1475774,"uid":2836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"721 811 812 818"},{"pid":"1915b877b6b51345b23cee8709bdb75c7e25c41b","tid":1475774,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efccf84834448e3d19f33be8a8336281b08b4cb3","tid":1475774,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:54:04.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2e092732c0713b46956515b105dd7b78eb3944","tid":1475774,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38825756f74fd41bf884e33bba7054d8bf5eee41","tid":1475774,"uid":144493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:54:36.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"55cc8110f36a658bceaae98e528fcb6e6023a5de","tid":1475774,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c3c934d692a2d1dee441f78b63ec590d9b2753","tid":1475774,"uid":267354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:02:46.000Z","msg":"推啊推啊"},{"pid":"3e5a7a0c3a98d64bf9076be9a795f93229a397b6","tid":1475774,"uid":178577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:05:52.000Z","msg":"推!!!!<br />\n記住所有警犬做過既所有野<br />\n遲d 一次過清算"},{"pid":"a422b7339afa27781d1e062e4086d16a65f5dc11","tid":1475774,"uid":42942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:00:26.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"537bd2057daa60660b79d8725fc568033fdcb5cc","tid":1475774,"uid":36735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:57:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}